# Zsh syntax highlighting plugin
# This plugin provides real-time syntax highlighting for commands as you type
# them in the Zsh command line, making it easier to spot errors and understand
# command structure.
#
# Features:
# - Real-time highlighting of commands, options, and arguments
# - Different colors for valid/invalid commands, quoted strings, etc.
# - Helps catch syntax errors before executing commands
# - Customizable color scheme and highlighting rules
#
# NOTE: This plugin should be loaded last among syntax-related plugins
# to ensure it works correctly with other command line enhancements

# Install the zsh-syntax-highlighting plugin using zinit
zinit light zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting